room_title: Escape room "(Wolf/Ram/Devil) The Mascot Rescue" by Escape on Purpose in Raleigh - Durham
room_description: The big game is today and you're getting ready for some great tailgating. Suddenly, you receive a text that your arch rivals have stolen your mascot and hidden it somewhere on their campus. Starting a big rivalry game without a mascot is just bad karma! It's up to you and your friends to retrieve your mascot before kickoff! You have 60 minutes...
